    <head><placeName key="PL000000008943">梁楊都湘宮寺</placeName><persName key="A003106">釋曇准</persName>傳九</head><p><anchor n="T.50.2060.0472a18"/><lb ed="T" n="0472a18"/><ptr target="fn02"/><persName key="A003106">釋曇准</persName>。姓弘。<placeName key="PL000000024116">魏郡湯陰</placeName>人。住<placeName key="PL000000024765">昌樂王寺</placeName>。出<lb ed="T" n="0472a19"/>家從<persName key="A003100">智誕法師</persName>受業。鑽研之勤眾<ptr target="fn08"/>皆弗及。<lb ed="T" n="0472a20"/>處靜味道。無風塵之志。善涅槃法華。聞諸<lb ed="T" n="0472a21"/><placeName key="PL000000023582">伊洛</placeName>。閑居遊思不交世務。承<persName key="A002655">齊竟陵王</persName>廣<lb ed="T" n="0472a22"/>延勝道盛興講說。遂南<ptr target="fn09"/>度止<placeName key="PL000000008943">湘宮寺</placeName>。處處<lb ed="T" n="0472a23"/>採聽隨席談論。雖逢塗阻未曾告勞。<persName key="A002264">次<lb ed="T" n="0472a24"/>公</persName>嘆曰。此<persName key="A003106">北道人</persName>。非直美容止善言笑。烈<lb ed="T" n="0472a25"/>亮恢廓雅有器度。至於言論深有情致。<persName key="A003057">齊<lb ed="T" n="0472a26"/><placeName key="PL000000019875">臨川</placeName>王蕭映</persName>。<persName key="A005086"><placeName key="PL000000028643">長沙</placeName>王蕭晃</persName>。厚相欽禮。<placeName key="PL000000016144">廬江</placeName><lb ed="T" n="0472a27"/><persName key="A003066">何<ptr target="fn10"/>點</persName><placeName key="PL000000009521">彭城</placeName><persName key="A005088">劉<ptr target="fn11"/>繒</persName>。並到房接足<ptr target="fn12"/>伸其戒誥。<lb ed="T" n="0472a28"/>講揚相繼成其業者二百餘人。以<date key="j19091921909574" from-iso="0515-02-02" to-iso="0516-02-19">天監十四<lb ed="T" n="0472a29"/>年</date>卒。春秋七十有七。時<placeName key="PL000000008943">寺</placeName>復有<persName key="A005087">智深</persName>比丘。<lb ed="T" n="0472b01"/>聰慧博識經論有功。天子王侯多所賓接。<lb ed="T" n="0472b02"/>性好直言無所推屑。每商略<ptr target="fn13"/>撿洗物<ptr target="fn14"/>不<lb ed="T" n="0472b03"/>有平。由是坎壈弘宣阻少。</p>
